OL,3,CNeonatal nurse accused of faking
OL,4,Cqualifications says there was bullying
OL,5,Con ward
OL,7,FA woman accused of faking her CV to
OL,8,Fget a job on a neonatal unit has said
OL,9,Fshe was suspended two days after
OL,10,Fraising concerns about bullying by "a
OL,11,Fmatriarch of nurses".
OL,13,FTanya Nasir defended her
OL,14,Fqualifications despite saying she
OL,15,Fcouldn't fully remember her degree
OL,16,Fgrade.
OL,18,FThe mother of two also told the jury
OL,19,Fshe'd decided to become a nurse in
OL,20,Forder to help others after living in a
OL,21,Frefuge.
