OL,5,Con ward
OL,7,FThe 45-year-old, originally from
OL,8,FHertfordshire, was suspended from the
OL,9,FPrincess of Wales Hospital in February
OL,10,F2020 after concerns were raised over
OL,11,F"inconsistencies" in her CV. She was
OL,12,Fappointed as a Band 7 Ward Manager on
OL,13,Fthe Bridgend hospital's neonatal ward,
OL,14,Fwhere she worked for 5 months from
OL,15,FSeptember 2019.
OL,17,FSpeaking for the first time at Cardiff
OL,18,FCrown Court today, Ms Nasir explained
OL,19,Fhow the unit "had a lot of problems"
OL,20,Fand described a "matriarch of nurses"
OL,21,Fwho perpetrated the alleged bullying.
