OL,7,F"There was a lot of work to do in
OL,8,Fterms of bringing things up to
OL,9,Fstandard. I wouldn't say I felt
OL,10,Fwelcomed by everybody. Some of the
OL,11,Fnurses were really being bullied -
OL,12,Fthey were working in fear," she said.
OL,14,FMs Nasir said she raised her concerns
OL,15,Funder the whistleblowing policy; but
OL,16,Ftwo days after meeting with the Deputy
OL,17,FHead of Nursing, she was informed that
OL,18,Fshe was being suspended.
