OL,7,FEarlier in the day, Ms Nasir told the
OL,8,Fcourt how she'd worked part-time - as
OL,9,Fa cleaner, dinner lady, and self-
OL,10,Femployed courier - alongside her
OL,11,Fstudies. When asked what the result of
OL,12,Fher first degree in Physics and
OL,13,FAstrophysics was - a qualification the
OL,14,Fcourt had previously heard was fake -
OL,15,Fshe replied, "A pass, I think. I can't
OL,16,Fremember."
