OL,7,FMs Nasir also told the jury she'd
OL,8,Fdecided to become a nurse after
OL,9,Fspending time in a refuge. She
OL,10,Fdescribed a "difficult relationship"
OL,11,Fwith her former partner and father of
OL,12,Fher children, calling him a "violent
OL,13,Falcoholic". She eventually left him
OL,14,Fand stayed in a refuge with her two
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,F"That was the reason I started nursing
OL,18,F- because of the people I met in the
OL,19,Frefuge. I wanted to help."
